article.description: Harrison Butler matched his season high with 21 points as Southern Utah defeated Drake 80-73 in overtime in the first round of the CIT on Friday night.
article.headline: Butler, Southern Utah beat Drake in CIT, 80-73 in OT
article.linkText: Butler, Southern Utah beat Drake in CIT, 80-73 in OT
article.story: CEDAR CITY, Utah -- Harrison Butler matched his season high with 21 points as Southern Utah defeated Drake 80-73 in overtime in the first round of the CIT on Friday night. Cameron Oluyitan had 15 points for Southern Utah (17-16). Dre Marin added 14 points. Brandon Better had 12 points for the hosts. Noah Thomas had 19 points for the Bulldogs (24-10). Liam Robbins added 14 points.
